attributes.Long form description: First, the student assembles the first leg of the middle tray. After that, the student assembles the second leg to the middle tray. Next, the student assembles the upper table to the legs. Then, the student assembles the third leg of the table and the middle tray. After that, the student assembles the fourth leg of the table and the middle tray. After that, the student screws all the remaining screws in all the legs and then tightens all of them with an allen wrench.
